IMEYA yeTheku ithembise ukuyisukumela ngokushesha inkinga yomphakathi waseReservoir Hills onqume ukuvala imigwaqo izolo ekuseni, ubhikishela ukunganakwa kwezindlu ohlala kuzo ezacekelwa phansi wumlilo. Phakathi kwezinkinga ezikhungethe lo mphakathi kubalwa ukungafakwa kwamapayipi endle nokungalungiswa kukagesi okubikwa ukuthi uqale ukuhlupha ngemva komlilo owashisa izindlu. UMnuz Mxolisi Kaunda, ohambele lo mphakathi  unxenxe uphiko lukagesi ukuthi luyilungise inkinga ekhungethe le ndawo. “Sivumelane ngomhlangano ozoba ngeSonto, esizolalela kuwo ezinye izimfuno zomphakathi. Amalungu omphakathi analo ilungelo lokuzwakalisa izikhalazo zawo kodwa siyawanxusa ukuthi aqikelele ukuthi awayilimazi impahla yomkhandlu,” kusho uKaunda. Eqhuba, uqinisekisile emalungwini omphakathi ukuthi umasipala uzozibophezela ekuphuthumiseni izidingo zawo. Uphinde wawatusa ukuthi asebenzise imigudu efanele uma efuna ukuzwakalisa izikhalo zawo. “Siwguhulumeni olalelayo futhi neminyango yethu ivulekile kulabo abafuna ukuxhumana nathi ngezimfuno zomphakathi,” kubeka imeya. 